NAME
        birthday
        birthday [mm/dd]
        birthday -clear

DESCRIPTION
        This command is available so you can set your birthday
        so others can see it while using the finger command.  It
        is not necessary to set your birthday.

SYNTAX
        birthday
                Shows your current set birthday, if any.

        birthday [mm/dd]
                Sets your birthday to [mm/dd]
                mm = month (1-12)
                dd = day (1-29, 30, or 31)

        birthday -clear
                Removes your set birthday.

SEE ALSO
	email, location, name, icq, webpage.
